Produk tissue ini juga lagi di promo-in, 10 pack cuma 4.000 atau 6.000
Pernah liat?

Nah, saat kamu klik keranjang kuning, kamu akan melihat produk yang berbeda alias mereknya Nice atau merek lain dengan harga lebih mahal seperti 40.000 atau 60.000.
Sebel kan?

Nah, akhirnya perjalanan gua kemarin setelah menuju ke Barat, gua menemukan Tissue-nya!
Sesuai sama Video! Hahaha...

I love love love this brand! Almost all the products I use are Valentino Beauty Pure. Not only is it easier to work with, it last soo much longer than some other brands I’ve used. Of course Valentino is a NO MMA product (Methyl methacrylate)…MMA is a bonding agent used in a lot of nail products. It’s a lot cheaper and adheres to the nail plate quicker, so a lot of salons use MMA products. But use of MMA as a nail product can cause nail damage and deformities in nail growth 😬 So I’ve invested in a brand without MMA that may be pricier but is definitely worth it! Your nails will thank you 🫶🏻. Plus the bottles just look cool😎
